{"_id":"rc5N1Ngelk0cuWzc","name":"Grim","type":"hindrance","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The hero is serious, taciturn, and finds mirth tiresome. She&rsquo;s @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Provoke]{Provoked} (see Savage Worlds) on any successful Taunt&mdash;whether the opponent has the Provoke Edge or not.</p>\n<p>Provoked characters subtract 2 from rolls to affect any opponent except the one who insulted him. This lasts until a Joker is drawn (by either side) or someone else successfully Taunts the dour ruffian.</p>\n<p>Grim also counts as a Requirement for the Menacing Edge (see Savage Worlds).</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"major":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.R5qLG8mL3RkCOB6I"},"cf":{"id":"temp_bf6w7lfm7uv"}}}
{"_id":"tIzTX3egp35NLLym","name":"Idealistic","type":"hindrance","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You see things in black and white and struggle with more nuanced dilemmas. Most of the time this is an admiral virtue, but it causes great issues when on the horns of a moral dilemma, such as whether to hand a starving poacher over to the king&rsquo;s guards or let him get away with his desperate but perhaps necessary crime.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"major":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fiUrTe9DdlxMMuOa"},"cf":{"id":"temp_bf6w7lfm7uv"}}}
{"_id":"v6JKrqba83DoMhev","name":"Blunderer","type":"hindrance","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Some heroes take a while to master their craft. Select a skill central to your character, such as Spellcasting for a wizard or Fighting for a warrior. The hero suffers a Critical Failure whenever she fails a roll and that skill die is a 1.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"major":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZAMlzK2tNh9QW3lg"},"cf":{"id":"temp_r5spssrhnxs"}}}
{"_id":"yliK2YkXzCLxrpBi","name":"Cursed","type":"hindrance","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Your heroine crossed some dark power and has forever after been marked by its tainted touch. Friendly powers, including those cast by allies or even herself, suffer a &ndash;2 penalty to the arcane skill roll. Worse, if the roll is a Critical Failure, the caster is Stunned!</p>\n<p>The penalty applies if the Cursed character is within an area effect power or targeted by the Additional Recipients modifier.</p>\n<p>The Curse has no effect on hostile power.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"major":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KPbqMA5tCYcdlhGe"},"cf":{"id":"temp_r5spssrhnxs"}}}
